<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When I create a project with Zend_Tool, for exemple:</p>

<p>$ cd /var/www
$ zf create project test</p>

<p>And after, in the browser I call: "http://localhost/test/public/error/error", I see 3 notices in the development enviroment:</p>

<p>Notice: Trying to get property of non-object in /var/www/test/application/controllers/ErrorController.php on line 10
Notice: Trying to get property of non-object in /var/www/test/application/controllers/ErrorController.php on line 33
Notice: Trying to get property of non-object in /var/www/test/application/controllers/ErrorController.php on line 36</p>

<p>This occurred becouse $this-&gt;_getParam('error_handler') is null when I am in "/error/error".</p>

<p>Before proceeding this line, must have a verification if $this-&gt;_getParam('error_handler') is instance of ArrayObject.</p>

